<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="uz">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Appeal Detail</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/appeal_detail.css" />
    <style>
        /* Inline CSS for quick preview, move to appeal_detail.css */
        
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        
        .header {
            background-color: #9c27b0;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        
        .header h2 {
            margin: 0;
        }
        
        .appeal-info {
            padding: 15px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
        }
        
        .appeal-info p {
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
        
        .appeal-info .category {
            color: #9c27b0;
        }
        
        .buttons {
            margin-top: 10px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }
        
        .btn {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            cursor: pointer;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .btn.accept {
            background-color: #4caf50;
        }
        
        .btn.reject {
            background-color: #f44336;
        }
        
        .history,
        .messages {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        
        .history .history-item {
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: #e0e0e0;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .messages textarea {
            width: calc(100% - 50px);
            padding: 10px;
            margin-top: 10px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
        }
        
        .messages button {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border: none;
            background-color: #9c27b0;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 4px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h2>Етказиб бериш бўйича</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="appeal-info">
            <p>Микроз савдо марказидан 20.02.2023-куни...</p>
            <p>Қўшимча маълумот: Янгона алоқа маркази</p>
            <p>Мурожаат қилувчи: Толипов Шухрат XXX</p>
            <p>Телефон номер: +998(91)-155-57-76</p>
            <p>Категория: <span class="category">Етказиб бериш бўйича</span></p>
            <div class="buttons">
                <button class="btn accept">Қабул қилинди</button>
                <button class="btn reject">Бекор қилиш</button>
            </div>
        </div>

